																	<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">5</div> <div class="vers-content">Gentleness of speech, how it wins friends everywhere, how it disarms its enemies! Never was a good man wanting for a gracious word.</div></div></td>
								</tr><tr>									<td><div class="vers"><div class="vers-no">6</div> <div class="vers-content">Be in peace with many, but let one of a thousand be thy counsellor.</div></div></td>
